f="https://www.nme.com/brands/sm-entertainment">SM Entertainment</a>新人男子乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/riize">RIIZE</a>将于今年四月开始他们的首次粉丝大会世界巡演，巡演地点遍及亚洲和美国。该组合将于四月至八月在东京、台北、新加坡等城市进行巡演，这是他们出道以来的首次海外头条演出。预计很快就会添加更多日期和站点，同时票务信息将“稍后”公布。检查<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_asia/news/music/riize-2024-riizing-day-fan-con-world-tour-asia-us-tickets-more-3596747">此页面</a>以获取最新更新。</p><h2> <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_asia/news/music/golden-wave-in-taiwan-2024-line-up-tickets-gi-dle-enhypen-3596699">新牛仔裤</a></h2><figure id="attachment_3598493" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3598493" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3598493" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/newjeans-billboard-women-in-music-group-of-the-year-speech.jpg" alt="Newjeans 广告牌年度女性音乐团体演讲" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/newjeans-billboard-women-in-music-group-of-the-year-speech.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/newjeans-billboard-women-in-music-group-of-the-year-speech-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/newjeans-billboard-women-in-music-group-of-the-year-speech-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/newjeans-billboard-women-in-music-group-of-the-year-speech-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/newjeans-billboard-women-in-music-group-of-the-year-speech-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/newjeans-billboard-women-in-music-group-of-the-year-speech-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3598493" class="wp-caption-text"> NewJeans 出席 2024 年公告牌女性音乐奖。图片来源：Getty Images/Rich Polk</figcaption></figure><p> <strong>“兔子营 2024”粉丝见面会 – 东京</strong></p><p><strong>2024 年 6 月</strong><br />周三 26 日至周四 27 – 日本东京，东京巨蛋</p><p>NewJeans 出人意料地宣布计划于今年某个时候在日本首次亮相，同时还宣布将于今年 6 月在日本首都东京巨蛋举行为期两天的粉丝见